<plot>The film 'Day' focuses on the bleak future of asylum seekers being held at a government centre for asylum seekers in the small town of Hendrik Ido Ambacht in the Netherlands and their hopes of leading a normal life one day. Their harrowing situation is symbolised by the daily life of Soran Ismail as he waits at the asylum seekers centre and the railway station.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?124139</url></doc>
